{"tid":1907563,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"誠意推介日本戀愛綜藝「想談一場偶像劇般的戀愛」","createTime":"2020-03-02T16:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T15:39:07.000Z","uid":275475,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"93384c78c0f42cf939d9c97257449da8cdeab735","tid":1907563,"uid":275475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"恋愛ドラマな恋がしたい〜Bang Ban Love〜<br />\n第一集link<br />\n中字<br />\n<a href=\"https://b23.tv/av85188929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fb23.tv%2Fav85188929&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=fb16d757\" target=\"_blank\">https://b23.tv/av85188929</a><br />\n<br />\n日文原版就要日本ip <br />\n星期日有新一集<br />\n<a href=\"https://abema.tv/video/title/90-1354\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fabema.tv%2Fvideo%2Ftitle%2F90-1354&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=3fe866e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://abema.tv/video/title/90-1354</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAbemaTV都玩咗好耐戀愛綜藝下<br />\n出名除咗呢個系列仲有別被月亮與狼醬所欺騙<br />\n億婚（幾正 睇d拜金女點分辨出演員定有錢佬）<br />\n<a href=\"https://b23.tv/av42710452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fb23.tv%2Fav42710452&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=3e29d1e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://b23.tv/av42710452</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恋愛ドラマな恋がしたい〜Bang Ban Love〜<br />\n<br />\n「想談一場偶像劇般的戀愛」呢個系列已經拍到第五季<br />\n我睇完第四季第五季覺得幾掂<br />\n<br />\n渡邊直美做旁述<br />\n三男三女邊拍單元劇加深感情<br />\n一邊拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD男仔有分演技型 高冷型 同不羈型<br />\n木村葉月夠可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前Dream5個日比美思好鬼正<br />\n阿佑夠專一<br />\n見證住佢地不斷係度組CP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係有番初戀嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576bb513891669d61231d6477a588119707d17de","tid":1907563,"uid":192929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93384c7